#define LST_NODE_STATE_COUNTER ( nd,
p   ) 
Value:
do {                                                    \
        if ((nd)->nd_state == LST_NODE_ACTIVE)          \
                (p)->nle_nactive ++;                    \
        else if ((nd)->nd_state == LST_NODE_BUSY)       \
                (p)->nle_nbusy ++;                      \
        else if ((nd)->nd_state == LST_NODE_DOWN)       \
                (p)->nle_ndown ++;                      \
        else                                            \
                (p)->nle_nunknown ++;                   \
        (p)->nle_nnode ++;                              \
} while (0)
